为你的产品（基于 Google Merchant Center/BigQuery 的全球商品趋势分析与选品平台）做 SEO 推广，建议聚焦以下关键词（keywords），覆盖跨境电商、选品、数据分析、趋势洞察等相关领域：

---

## 核心关键词（Core Keywords）

- product trends
- hot products
- trending products
- global product trends
- ecommerce trends
- market trends
- product analytics
- product ranking
- product insights
- product demand analysis
- product data analysis
- product research
- product intelligence
- product database

---

## 长尾关键词（Long-tail Keywords）

- best selling products by country
- fastest growing products 2024
- global ecommerce product trends
- Google Merchant Center data analysis
- BigQuery product analytics
- cross-border ecommerce product research
- how to find trending products
- product demand forecasting
- weekly product ranking
- product category trends
- discover new products for ecommerce
- data-driven product selection
- product trend dashboard
- real-time product trends
- product market insights tool

