## 品牌词（Brand Keywords）

- EcomPulse
- EcomPulse trends
- EcomPulse analytics

---

## 推荐做法

1. **首页 Title/Description**  
   - Title: "Global Product Trends & Analytics | EcomPulse"
   - Description: "Discover trending products, analyze global market trends, and make data-driven decisions with EcomPulse. Powered by Google Merchant Center and BigQuery."

2. **页面内容自然嵌入关键词**  
   - 在首页、explore、how-it-works、pricing 等页面的标题、副标题、描述、FAQ、博客等自然融入上述关键词。

3. **Meta Keywords（虽然现代SEO权重低，但可补充）**  
   - `<meta name="keywords" content="product trends, trending products, ecommerce trends, product analytics, global product trends, product research, product ranking, product insights, Google Merchant Center, BigQuery, cross-border ecommerce, data-driven product selection, EcomPulse">`

4. **内容营销**  
   - 发布“2024全球热销产品趋势”、“如何用数据选品”、“Google Merchant Center数据分析实战”等博客/文章，进一步覆盖长尾关键词。

---

如需为你生成首页 SEO meta 标签或页面内容建议，请告知！